properties.Name: ChannelCategory
properties.Description:
There are three categories of channels:

(1) Sales Channel
(2) Distribution Channel
(3) Combined 'Sales and Distribution'

A single entity may be either a Sales Channel, a Distribution Channel or both.

Sales Channel - A sales channel 'sells' products, goods or services.   

Distribution Channel - A distribution channel 'distributes' products, goods or services and may or may not have sold them initially.     

Combined Channels - Some channel perform both functions and sell and distribute products, goods or services.
